                  $=6^2-2 \times 6 \times (8a+b)+(8a+b)^2$ $=36-2 \times 6 \times 8a-2 \times 6 \times b+(8a)^2+2 \times 8ab+b^2$</span>
                <!--ここまで-->
              </div>
            </span>
            $=36-96a-12b+64a^2+16ab+b^2$
            <br><br>$\{10-(9a+b)\}^2$
            <span class="hidden_box3">
