            $=100-180a-20b+81a^2+18ab+b^2$<br><br>
            よって<br>
            $E(a,b)=(1)\underline{\{&emsp;&emsp;\}}^2 + \{7-(6a+b)\}^2 + \{9-(7a+b)\}^2 $ $+ \{6-(8a+b)\}^2 + \{10-(9a+b)\}^2$<br>
